Hello.

35
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:56,240
Is there a patient

36
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:56,960
by the name Su Xie Yi

37
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:58,280
or Li Ze Liang?

38
00:02:58,560 --> 00:02:59,599
Hold on, I'll check it for you.

39
00:02:59,599 --> 00:03:00,080
Okay.

