00:38:52,390 --> 00:38:54,980
♪Dwelling in the past♪

797
00:38:55,390 --> 00:38:58,460
♪No, it's not too hard♪

798
00:39:25,510 --> 00:39:27,260
♪How are you?♪

799
00:39:27,560 --> 00:39:29,210
♪How are you with him?♪

